The paper also discusses optimization and generalization guarantees for neural networks, which are important topics in optimization and theoretical computer science. Therefore, it is also possible that the paper could be categorized as cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). 

Additionally, the paper focuses on the problem of linearly separable data, which is a common problem in computer vision and pattern recognition. Therefore, it is also possible that the paper could be categorized as cs.CV (Computer Vision) or cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
